00:27:11.510 --> 00:27:15.800
on when I was learning
the ropes of design sprint

00:27:15.800 --> 00:27:18.510
facilitation, where I bit
off way more than I could

00:27:18.510 --> 00:27:20.690
chew, a little bit unknowingly.

