00:27:37.090 --> 00:27:41.570
It was like the second
sprint I facilitated.

00:27:41.570 --> 00:27:44.280
And it had all of the things.

00:27:44.280 --> 00:27:46.550
It had all of the earmarks
that I should have--

00:27:46.550 --> 00:27:51.500
I now know to be on the lookout
for-- of a lot of baggage

00:27:51.500 --> 00:27:53.340
between different parts
of the organization.

00:27:53.340 --> 00:27:56.360
A lot of people with very
specific ideas to the points

00:27:56.360 --> 00:27:58.810
that both of you have made.

00:27:58.810 --> 00:28:02.420
Also when I started getting
involved in the project,

00:28:02.420 --> 00:28:04.220
