their own ideas

00:28:24.590 --> 00:28:27.359
and kept bringing it
back to themselves.

00:28:27.359 --> 00:28:29.150
And just with the sheer
size of that group,

00:28:29.150 --> 00:28:32.150
it's almost impossible to track
down and sort of pay attention

00:28:32.150 --> 00:28:33.980
to everyone's thoughts.

00:28:33.980 --> 00:28:36.560
So I had these little moments
where I'd like, OK, break time.

00:28:36.560 --> 00:28:40.330
