00:29:03.140 --> 00:29:06.140
I also paid a lot more attention
to some of those unspoken

00:29:06.140 --> 00:29:11.210
signals of democratic thinking
to direct attention to the ways

00:29:11.210 --> 00:29:15.170
that people were aligning,
even as this one person was

00:29:15.170 --> 00:29:17.330
disrupting and derailing.

00:29:17.330 --> 00:29:21.830
And in some instances, I needed
to even take that person aside

00:29:21.830 --> 00:29:23.330
and have some hard
conversations.

00:29:23.330 --> 00:29:25.704
And I was just like, listen,
this is either going to work

00:29:25.704 --> 00:29:27.240
or it's not.

00:29:27.240 --> 00:29:30.470
And somehow, near the end of
