00:29:30.470 --> 00:29:34.254
And there was enough visibility
into people's shared vision

00:29:34.254 --> 00:29:36.170
of what was going to be
built that we ended up

00:29:36.170 --> 00:29:39.590
with a pretty amazingly
successful process that right

00:29:39.590 --> 00:29:42.390
now is being experimented
with across the company, which

00:29:42.390 --> 00:29:44.044
was pretty cool.

00:29:44.044 --> 00:29:44.710
KAI HALEY: Cool.

00:29:44.710 --> 00:29:49.340
It Sounds like you really
